Simple Table (Easy to Remember)
Type	Meaning
Node Affinity	Pod chooses node
Pod Affinity	Pod wants nearby pod
Pod Anti-Affinity	Pod wants separation
Required	Must follow
Preferred	Best effort
One-Line Interview Answers

Affinity helps performance

Anti-Affinity improves availability

Node affinity replaces nodeSelector

Pod anti-affinity avoids single point of failure

